{"about_the_game":"Dragon Bobby is a uniquely beautiful game with third-person exploration and puzzles that tells the story of a man's life from birth. You control a dragon that is an analogy of this man in the story. A true reflection on life.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656930/extras/1-No-Gif1.png?t=1723646561\" /><br><br>Explore a world with beautiful graphics. As the dragon grows, it acquires the ability to explore the world by land, water and air.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656930/extras/2-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1723646561\" /><br><br>A unique game, which in parallel shows the passages of a man's life and the challenges he faces in it. The story makes us reflect on ourselves and our choices and actions.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656930/extras/3-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1723646561\" /><br><br>Key features:<br>- Explore a world with wonderful landscapes on an exciting Journey<br>- Solve puzzles and collect hidden memories <br>- Experience the life story of Bobby, a man represented in the game by a dragon that you control.<br>- Stunning soundtrack by acclaimed artists<br>- A game based on exploration, puzzle and narrative games such as &quot;The First Tree&quot;, &quot;Spirit of the North&quot;, &quot;Lost Ember&quot; and &quot;Journey&quot;.  If you liked some of these games, you'll love &quot;Dragon Bobby&quot;<br><br>- This is an indie game created by a single person. I programmed, did the game design and wrote the story, while my children helped me by testing the gameplay.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656930/extras/4-No-Gif.png?t=1723646561\" /><br><br>ATTENTION: This game does not use any A.I. resources. All the photos used in it are royalty free and taken from